{"tid":429264,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每次都阿媽嘈完交都會後悔","createTime":"2017-10-08T17:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T18:58:21.000Z","uid":120202,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b18fea1f03560e55748a76295dec1c3646c45c6d","tid":429264,"uid":120202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:23:51.000Z","msg":"我都知佢做所有野出發點都係關心我<br />\n但有時真係令人好炆好燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日借d意偷睇我櫃桶<br />\n一有d咩事又周圍問親戚 明明我唔想將件事揚開<br />\n同一樣野叫左佢唔好咁做 但永遠都唔聽 第二日照做<br />\n個刻真係忍唔住爆曬出黎狂罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今朝先罵完 宜家夜晚執野無意中見到小學d功課同相簿<br />\n我係入面寫媽媽有幾好 要努力報答媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而每一張我細個既相背後 都有阿媽寫既記錄 攝於幾年幾月 希望阿仔快高長大<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻好內疚今朝罵得咁大聲 <br />\n其實我真係唔想咁罵你 但我牛脾氣好難改 好難忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係想你聽我一次話 唔好做d令我嬲既野姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8776bb4747c6e9879379fb5554297cd8a16a864","tid":429264,"uid":120202,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:25:44.000Z","msg":"都唔知由幾時開始 我同你既交流除左今晚食咩 幾點翻 就係為d小事罵交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好憎自己 點解唔可以躺開心扉 同阿媽變翻以前咁frd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fe5daa4585d9a2aba59a425ec48ba9d2f19e4a","tid":429264,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:27:01.000Z","msg":"你要體諒佢<br />\n但同時要諗下咩原因導致佢咁<br />\n會唔會可能精神健康出現問題<br />\n定純綷更好年期暴躁"},{"pid":"e396687b845916d49932077d2b0e50b02eed2e1f","tid":429264,"uid":86151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次用d衰語氣對住阿媽之後都會好內疚<br />\n但當下真係忍唔到"},{"pid":"f151b0f0147f72bd73e8807b6b6777d7f8249503","tid":429264,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:30:08.000Z","msg":"我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  次次都好內疚"},{"pid":"b5ad283b26daae0185a537f80134c7c99115dc66","tid":429264,"uid":121610,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"唉一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時仲爆哂粗 明明好少事<br />\n但真係好煩<br />\n點先可以改善"},{"pid":"d004f22571e89ef2a923fcc85153ac34353e2a3b","tid":429264,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次用d衰語氣對住阿媽之後都會好內疚<br />\n但當下真係忍唔到</blockquote><br />\n嗰刻你同阿媽嘈實忍唔到<br />\n除非你eq好高<br />\n之後內疚因為你都知自己有唔啱<br />\n我都會咁<br />\n有啲人話閙交嗰陣<br />\n其中一方行開下會好啲<br />\n下次可以試下 （或者返入房）"},{"pid":"d733be4f420418e61962117bd3556ec7513b3b2c","tid":429264,"uid":121958,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:37:03.000Z","msg":"以前都同呀媽每晚喊交 喊到好癡線 嗰下先中三<br />\n後尾靠中學missy同我地傾先解決咗<br />\n揾第三者幫下手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa206f95bdb071226162a7c6d09961e38c60132","tid":429264,"uid":84412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:40:18.000Z","msg":"下 偷睇你野喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係唔鬧呀？<br />\n要friend到都要佢識基本尊重啦"},{"pid":"033fd378d0be61bde787ca168b714db4a109466c","tid":429264,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前都同呀媽每晚喊交 喊到好癡線 嗰下先中三<br />\n後尾靠中學missy同我地傾先解決咗<br />\n揾第三者幫下手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmiss點幫？"},{"pid":"0f2dcad1c6bd406b4395542754b1aff65f05280b","tid":429264,"uid":64343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,